Method Detail

run

public OptInfo run(DepotLinkedList mainDepots)
This module attempts to combine any two trucks. Only the trucks that are not of the largest truck type can be used in a combination. This method does the selection of the trucks that used in the combination and calls the AttemptToCombineTrucks() to do the actual combination. The cheapest combination found is used. Author: Dilsara Pathirana

Overrides:
run in class MixedFleetOptimization
Returns:
Boolean value stating whether the module found any improvements

java.lang.Exception

AttemptToCombineTrucks

public boolean AttemptToCombineTrucks(Truck firstTruck,
                                      Truck secondTruck,
                                      Depot thisDepot)
This method will attempt to combine the two trucks firstTruck and secondTruck from the depot thisDepot. The new combined truck is used only if the combination produces the cheaper result.

Parameters:
firstTruck - First truck to be used in combination
secondTruck - Second truck to be used in combination
thisDepot - Depot that these two trucks belong to
Returns:
Boolean value stating whether the combination was successful
